      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just stuck in this endless loop. another job lost, another person leaving, another day where i just feel like a burden to everyone around me. it doesnt matter what i do or how hard i try, i just end up right back here at zero. it's like i'm broken and there's no way to fix it.",
