      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just \"negative thoughts\" though. it's reality. every time i think i've made progress, something happens and i'm back in the exact same spot. it's like the universe wants me to fail. i'm just tired of fighting a battle that's already been lost. there's no \"step back\" when you're already at the bottom.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
