      "content": "It can feel suffocating when the universe seems to be constantly pushing you back, making it hard to catch your breath. It's understandable that you're exhausted from trying to overcome the same obstacles again and again. At times like these, acknowledging your emotions instead of trying to reason with them can be a powerful release. Allow yourself to feel the weight of reality, but don't give up on yourself just yet - sometimes, the universe's pushback can be exactly what leads you to the next part of your journey.",
      "source": "target",
